<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yé hé huá a nǐ yǐ jīng jiàn chá wǒ 迦南1165</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yé hé huá a nǐ yǐ jīng jiàn chá wǒ, yé hé huá a nǐ zǎo yǐ rèn shì wǒ.
 wǒ zuò xià qǐ lái nǐ dōu xiǎo dé, nǐ zài yuǎn chù zhī dào wǒ zài xiǎng shén me.
 nǐ dōu xì chá wǒ xíng lù tǎng wò, yě shēn zhī wǒ yī qiè suǒ xíng suǒ zuò. wǒ shé
 tóu shàng de huà, nǐ méi yǒu yī jù bù zhī nǐ zài wǒ qián hòu huán rào wǒ. zài mǔ
 fù zhōng nǐ yǐ fù bì wǒ, wèi chéng xíng shí nǐ yǐ kàn jiàn wǒ. wǒ yào
 chēng xiè nǐ, cóng rì chū dào rì luò nǐ chuàng zào wǒ yīn nǐ ràng wǒ cún huó.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1165</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>